#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "⚠️ Sensitive Content Notice"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This module shares basic self-defence ideas. It cannot prepare you for every danger. If a partner or spouse is hurting you, fighting back can sometimes make things more dangerous. The safest choice is often to get away and get help.\n"
"\n"
"If you need support, see the “Support Contacts” section in the @global.app_name Library for help."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Our topic today is protecting yourself.\n"
"\n"
"To keep our teens safe, we need to understand their reality and the potential risky situations they can find themselves in.\n"
"\n"
"We can help our teens know how to use their thoughts, voice, AND body in dangerous situations. It makes a big difference!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why is discussing safety with your teen important? Tap play to find out"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Our topic is staying safe.\n"
"\n"
"Our safety and our children’s safety is important. We may need to have discussions with our children about their safety, and how they can keep themselves safe always."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"We’ve looked at warning signs in the Teen Safety lesson. Now let’s think—what can we do if we don’t feel safe?\n"
"\n"
"If you feel unsafe, you can say or do anything to stay safe. The goal is to get away!\n"
"\n"
"Think about the moment when @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name was pressured into a car.\n"
"\n"
"How could she use her voice to get away?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Find a chair and pretend it is the attacker. Practise saying/doing these responses:**\n"
"\n"
"- 🔈 Yell: \"No!\" \n"
"- 🆘 Call for help: \"Someone help me!\" \n"
"- ⚠️ Warn of consequences: \"I will call the police if you touch me again.\"\n"
"- ⛔ Name the behaviour: \"Do not touch my bum.” or “Do not yell at me.”\n"
"- 😳 Act crazy: Make a crazy scream or act like a gorilla!\n"
"- 🚶🏾‍♀️ Pretend to go along to buy time: “I will do anything you want, just please don’t hurt me.”\n"
"- 🤡 Use humour: “No lift for me, thanks. Last time I got a lift I threw up EVERYWHERE!”\n"
"- 📱 Give something to get what you want: “I will give you my phone if you let me go.”"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When our voice does not stop the situation, we can use our bodies to defend ourselves."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**EYES**\n"
"- Use your fingers as claws and scratch the attacker’s face as hard as possible.\n"
"\n"
"- Push your thumbs into the eye sockets of your attacker and then outward towards the sides of their head.\n"
"\n"
"**THROAT**\n"
"- Push your finger into the hole at the bottom of the attacker’s throat.\n"
"\n"
"- Punch the throat with your fist or the back of your elbow.\n"
"\n"
"**GROIN**\n"
"- Kick the attacker’s groin with your knee, or punch it with your fist or elbow.\n"
"\n"
"- Grab, squeeze, twist and pull the attacker’s testicles with your hand.\n"
"\n"
"**KNEES**\n"
"- Kick against your attacker's knee with your foot."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take a look at the image and these examples to see how you can use the weak spots or targets on your attacker’s body."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Learn how to protect yourself by knowing weak spots on an attacker’s body:"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Weak Spots"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**TEMPLES**\n"
"- Punch the attacker’s temples with your fist or the back of your elbow.\n"
"\n"
"**NOSE** \n"
"- Punch the attacker’s nose with your fist or the back of your elbow.\n"
"\n"
"**EARS**\n"
"- With flat hands, smack the attacker’s ears from both sides as hard as possible. You can also pull or twist them.\n"
"\n"
"**RIBS**\n"
"- Punch the attacker in the ribs with your fist or the back of your elbow.\n"
"\n"
"**FINGERS**\n"
"- Pull the attacker's pinky or little finger away from the other fingers hard and fast (it breaks easily).\n"
"\n"
"**SHINS**\n"
"- Kick against the attacker’s shins as hard as you can.\n"
"\n"
"**TOP OF FEET**\n"
"- Lift your foot and stomp your heel on the top of your attacker’s foot."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is an additional image to show you more examples of how you can use the weak spots or targets on your attacker’s body."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some skills to help you and your teen stay safe!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "KNOW IT"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Know the difference between healthy and unhealthy relationships. If someone hurts you, it is never your fault.\n"
"\n"
"You are allowed to say and do what is needed to stay safe and get away—don’t worry about what others think.\n"
"\n"
"You are worth defending. You are strong and powerful."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEE IT"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"If someone says or does something that makes you feel uncomfortable, it’s not okay. We all have the right to feel safe, especially at home.\n"
"\n"
"See the warning signs and trust your feelings. If you feel unsafe, the goal is to get away."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SAY IT"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Your voice can help stop an attack. Yell, call for help, warn, act, or use humour to stay safe.\n"
"\n"
"Be clear, confident, and direct—use your words, body, and eyes."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "DO IT"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"If your voice doesn’t help, use your body.\n"
"\n"
"Know the strong parts of your body you can use, and where on the attacker’s body you can hit to stop them. Use what you can to protect yourself and get away."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"In danger, it’s normal to freeze or feel unsure. These tools can help you and your teen stay safe.\n"
"\n"
"If you or your teen are hurt, it is never your fault. Talk to someone you trust.\n"
"\n"
"As a caregiver, let your teen know they can always tell you anything, and you’ll find a solution together."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This week’s home activity is to talk with your teen about this Protecting Yourself module.\n"
"\n"
"These conversations can be hard at first, but they give your teen important skills for staying safe. You can do it!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember to:**\n"
"\n"
"⚠️ Spot warning signs: Talk with your teen about places, people, or situations that may not be safe. Remind them to trust their feelings.\n"
"📣 Use your voice: Practise saying “no” or asking for help.\n"
"🙅🏽‍♀️ Use your body: Make a plan together for how to leave or protect yourself."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you discuss the Protecting Yourself module with your teen this week?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fantastic! Going through this module’s skills makes it more likely your teen will act quickly and protect themselves when it matters most."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That is a good start! Every time you talk about safety, you make it easier for your teen to trust their instincts and speak up. Keep going!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Safety talks can feel hard, but even one conversation can prepare your teen for real situations. You can try again when you are ready."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Helping your teen learn to notice danger, speak up, and protect themselves builds real confidence.\n"
"\n"
"Practising together makes it more likely they will act when something feels wrong."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_9.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_daughter_9.name used her voice to stay safe"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It helped me a lot that I learnt I can use my voice to stay safe. A while ago, I was walking home alone and some man began to follow me and I felt scared. My father taught me that the most important thing is to be safe, so I turned around and said loud and clear ‘Why are you following me, I don’t want that’. It really surprised the man and even some other people looked at us, so the man walked away. I felt so relieved and even told my father. He said I did well and I felt really good. Before, I would have been too scared, also what other people think, but now I feel confident."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
